          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Using the various (Livermore and Saclay)  experiments",
                " data  for  total  photoneutron  yield reaction cross",
                " sections  SIG(g,xn)  and   the   modern   model   of",
                " photonuclear   reaction   based  on  the  Fermi  gas",
                " densities equations the evaluated data for (g,n) and",
                " (g,2n) reaction cross sections were obtained.",
                "Evaluated cross   sections   are   consistent    with",
                " experimental Livermore data and contradict to Saclay",
                " ones."
              ]
            }
          ],
